{"tid":97264,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"林鄭500元予中國行乞婦　胡國興：「乞取施捨」屬違法","createTime":"2017-01-27T13:57:44.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-28T14:00:56.000Z","uid":53003,"like":31,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"40f7713dafea328805b2d52dc668395fda2262bd","tid":97264,"uid":53003,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T13:57:44.000Z","msg":"行政長官參選人林鄭月娥今日到訪沙田，向一位據稱來自湖北的行乞老婦給予500元。另一參選人、退休法官胡國興在facebook表示，根據簡易程序治罪條例26A條，「乞取施捨」是違法行為。<br />\n<br />\n　　胡國興期望社署社工，即使在新年假期，也可以儘快瞭解、跟進婆婆情況，確保她得到合適照顧。要設法真正幫到婆婆才是辦法。<br />\n<br />\n　　林鄭月娥競選辦回應指，林太善心先行，年三十見到婆婆行乞，感到心酸因而向她施予，忽略可能引起批評；林太當時只想令到婆婆在歲晚感覺好一點。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E7%89%B9%E9%A6%96%E9%81%B8%E6%88%B0-%E6%9E%97%E9%84%AD500%E5%85%83%E4%BA%88%E8%A1%8C%E4%B9%9E%E5%A9%A6-%E8%83%A1%E5%9C%8B%E8%88%88-%E4%B9%9E%E5%8F%96%E6%96%BD%E6%8D%A8-%E5%B1%AC%E9%81%95%E6%B3%95-122800399.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E7%2589%25B9%25E9%25A6%2596%25E9%2581%25B8%25E6%2588%25B0-%25E6%259E%2597%25E9%2584%25AD500%25E5%2585%2583%25E4%25BA%2588%25E8%25A1%258C%25E4%25B9%259E%25E5%25A9%25A6-%25E8%2583%25A1%25E5%259C%258B%25E8%2588%2588-%25E4%25B9%259E%25E5%258F%2596%25E6%2596%25BD%25E6%258D%25A8-%25E5%25B1%25AC%25E9%2581%2595%25E6%25B3%2595-122800399.html&d=za12ywSivCnp80l6%2BeUfgwT5PszEexF2%2B6H4LydsHP4%3D&h=fcabfb43\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E7%89%B9%E9%A6%96%E9%81%B8%E6%88%B0-%E6%9E%97%E9%84%AD500%E5%85%83%E4%BA%88%E8%A1%8C%E4%B9%9E%E5%A9%A6-%E8%83%A1%E5%9C%8B%E8%88%88-%E4%B9%9E%E5%8F%96%E6%96%BD%E6%8D%A8-%E5%B1%AC%E9%81%95%E6%B3%95-122800399.html</a>"},{"pid":"7a90e3fd35f3c7593a639e706ca53d211c488214","tid":97264,"uid":49392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T14:01:57.000Z","msg":"14年林鄭講過幾多次法治話?"},{"pid":"abae197544f0a511418d71a95c3d51d8881ef375","tid":97264,"uid":29804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T14:02:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>行政長官參選人林鄭月娥今日